'''拥抱、扩展再消灭'''（{{lang-en|'''Embrace, extend, and extinguish'''}}<ref name=DeadlyEmbrace>{{cite news|url=http://www.economist.com/displayStory.cfm?Story_ID=298112|title=Deadly embrace|publisher=The Economist|date=2000-03-30|accessdate=2006-03-31|archive-date=2010-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100301105543/http://www.economist.com/displayStory.cfm?Story_ID=298112|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最後一個詞也作{{lang|en|'''exterminate'''}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.zdnet.com/2100-3513_22-996528.html|title=Microsoft limits XML in Office 2003|accessdate=2006-03-31| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050922005808/http://news.zdnet.com/2100-3513_22-996528.html| archivedate = September 22, 2005}}</ref>，或按'''{{lang|en|extinguish}}'''译为'''扑灭'''）是[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]在[[微软|微软]]公司内部发现的一句短语<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usdoj.gov/atr/cases/f2600/v-a.pdf|title=US Department of Justice Proposed Findings of Fact—Revised|website=Usdoj.gov|accessdate=2016-04-28|archive-date=2012-03-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66N1vT0bU?url=http://www.justice.gov/atr/cases/f2600/v-a.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usdoj.gov/atr/cases/f2600/2613.htm|title=US Department of Justice Proposed Findings of Fact|website=Usdoj.gov|accessdate=2016-04-28|archive-date=2012-03-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66N1vutmc?url=http://www.justice.gov/atr/cases/f2600/2613.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，表述了微软的一种市场战略，即：首先接纳广泛使用的技术标准，将产品推入市场，然后在产品中加入自己的[[私有软件|專利]]擴充，最终用这些非标准的專利扩展使竞争对手处于不利地位之中。

== 詞源 ==
「擁抱再扩展」一詞第一次在微軟公司之外提到是在1996年的一篇標題為《明天就是全球資訊網！PC巨頭微軟打算統治互聯網》的[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]文章中<ref>{{cite news|date=July 16, 1996|author=John Markoff|publisher=New York Times|title=Tomorrow, the World Wide Web! Microsoft, the PC King, Wants to Reign Over the Internet|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1996/07/16/business/tomorrow-world-wide-web-microsoft-pc-king-wants-reign-over-internet.html?pagewanted=all|accessdate=2013-07-25|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309064746/https://www.nytimes.com/1996/07/16/business/tomorrow-world-wide-web-microsoft-pc-king-wants-reign-over-internet.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其作者{{link-en|約翰·馬爾科夫|John Markoff}}寫道：「微軟的批評者們擔心說，這家公司不止是擁抱、擴充了互聯網，更有將互聯網吞入口中的意願。」「擁抱再扩展」一詞也見於微軟員工Dean Ballard所作的一首幽默勵志歌曲<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.businessweek.com/1996/29/b34841.htm|title=Inside Microsoft (Part 1)|first=Kathy|last=Rebello|date=1996-07-15|accessdate=2006-03-31|publisher=Business Week|archive-date=2011-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110103014957/http://www.businessweek.com/1996/29/b34841.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>和紐約時報對[[史蒂夫·巴爾默|史蒂夫·巴爾默]]的採訪中<ref>Steve Lohr, "Preaching from the Ballmer Pulpit". ''New York Times'', Sunday, January 28, 2007. pp. 3-1, 3-8, 3-9.</ref>。

「拥抱、扩展再消灭」的版本首見於[[合众国诉微软案|合众国诉微软案]]這個{{tsl|en|United States antitrust law|美國反托拉斯法|反托拉斯案}}中。當時[[英特尔|英特尔]]的副總裁{{link-en|史蒂文·麥吉迪|Steven McGeady}}證言稱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/msdoj/transcripts/1110a.doc|title=Steven McGeady court testimony|website=Cyber.law.harvard.edu|accessdate=2006-03-31|archive-date=2011-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514052935/http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/msdoj/transcripts/1110a.doc|dead-url=no}} ([[DOC格式|DOC]] format)</ref>，微軟副總裁{{link-en|保羅·馬里茨|Paul Maritz}}於1985年與英特爾開會時用這個詞彙描述了微軟對於[[網景|網景]]、[[Java平臺|Java]]、[[網際網路|網際網路]]採用的策略<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/msdoj/transcript/summaries2.html|title=United States v. Microsoft: Trial Summaries (page 2)|website=Cyber.law.harvard.edu|accessdate=2006-03-31|archive-date=2011-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110504030046/http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/msdoj/transcript/summaries2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://reactor-core.org/in-microsoft-we-trust.html|title=IN MICROSOFT WE TRUST|accessdate=2006-03-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20050419194550/http://reactor-core.org/in-microsoft-we-trust.html|archivedate=2005年4月19日|df=}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>。

== 策略 ==
3E戰略分成三個階段進行：<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hr.com/servlets/sfs?&t=/Default/gateway&i=1116423256281&b=1116423256281&application=story&active=no&ParentID=1119278102301&StoryID=1119649742078|title=Embrace, Extend, Extinguish (IT Vendor Strategies)|website=Hr.com|accessdate=2007-10-14|archive-date=2006-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060428084112/http://www.hr.com/servlets/sfs|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
;擁抱:開發某個基本相容競爭者產品或開放標準的軟體。
;擴充:增加不屬於競爭者產品或開放標準的額外功能，為原版軟體的顧客製造互換性問題。
;消滅:等到市場佔有率提升推動之前的擴充成為[[事實標準|事實標準]]，競爭者就會因為不支援或不能支援新擴充被擠出市場。

微軟聲稱，其原本戰略並非要打壓競爭，而只是行使了自由裁量權來實作認為客戶需要的功能<ref>{{cite web|url=http://openacademy.mindef.gov.sg/openacademy/Learning%20Resources/Microsoft/words/words_4.htm |title=U.S. v. Microsoft: We're Defending Our Right to Innovate |website=Openacademy.mindef.gov.sg |accessdate=2007-03-29 |deadurl=unfit |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070329064009/http://openacademy.mindef.gov.sg/openacademy/Learning%20Resources/Microsoft/words/words_4.htm |archivedate=March 29, 2007 }}</ref>。

== 例子 ==
* '''浏览器：'''
** 反垄断案件的原告宣称微软在[[IE浏览器|IE浏览器]]添加[[ActiveX|ActiveX控件]]的支持来破坏[[網景_(瀏覽器)|Netscape浏览器]]的兼容性，后者使用基于[[Java|Java]]和Netscape自己的[[插件|插件]]系统的组件。
** [[CSS|CSS]]、data:等等：原有的关于Netscape的反垄断诉讼之后，浏览器公司[[Opera软件|Opera软件]]向[[欧盟|欧盟]]对微软提起反垄断诉讼並“呼吁微软坚持自己的公开声明支持这些标准，而不是用它臭名昭著的“拥抱、扩展和消滅”战略来扼杀他们”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.opera.com/pressreleases/en/2007/12/13/|title=files antitrust complaint with the EU|accessdate=2016-04-28|date=2007-12-13|publisher=Opera|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080906145643/http://www.opera.com/pressreleases/en/2007/12/13/|archive-date=2008-09-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
